				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=53948&amp;sid=94f3c2d8975e72e170c644b6d1cad657#53948"><img src="templates/SpacePilot3K/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Thu Feb 16, 2006 7:30 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: </span></td>
